{"tid":689144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務卿: 「六四」之魂還未安息, 促中國政府尊重人權","createTime":"2018-06-04T00:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T11:08:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f35b8ed1f97d098a90a11c12b751bffd2327cab8","tid":689144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:49:16.000Z","msg":"六四同中國人權唔關香港人事, 關美國咩事?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1857896/蓬佩奧發聲明%3A六四之魂還未安息\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1857896%2F%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%253A%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%B9%8B%E9%AD%82%E9%82%84%E6%9C%AA%E5%AE%89%E6%81%AF&d=vzNaOYh9vM3wKlqSaL%2BMtp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=87720e44\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1857896/蓬佩奧發聲明%3A六四之魂還未安息</a></span><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧發聲明:六四之魂還未安息 時事脈搏 | 今日 08:04<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧(Mike Pompeo)在六四事件29周年發表聲明，指記得當年天安門廣場及周邊地區的和平示威，遭到暴力鎮壓，有無辜生命的慘痛損失。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，正如2010年諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波缺席頒獎禮的講話提及，六四之魂仍還沒有安息。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，美國與國際社會敦促北京政府，公開當年死者、被拘留或失蹤者的情况，釋放被判監人士，停止滋擾示威者及他們的家屬。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>蓬佩奧強調，美國認為保護人權是所有國家的基本責任，敦促中國政府尊重所有公民的普遍權利及基本自由。</strong>"},{"pid":"5bb3ee6cc1077cf1409e4658cb74efe80235ad9c","tid":689144,"uid":81876,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"f35b8ed1f97d098a90a11c12b751bffd2327cab8","tid":689144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:49:16.000Z","msg":"六四同中國人權唔關香港人事, 關美國咩事?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1857896/蓬佩奧發聲明%3A六四之魂還未安息\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1857896%2F%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%253A%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%B9%8B%E9%AD%82%E9%82%84%E6%9C%AA%E5%AE%8